《'''玩美自信'''》（{{lang-en|Confident}}）是美国唱作歌手[[黛米·洛瓦托|黛米·洛瓦托]]的歌曲，是她2015年{{le|玩美自信 (专辑)|Confident (album)|同名}}第五张录音室专辑的第二首单曲<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6700433/demi-lovato-confident-single-listen-stream|title=Demi Lovato Drops New Single 'Confident': Listen|last=Weiner|first=Natalie|work=Billboard|agency=Prometheus Global Media|accessdate=2017-01-07|archive-date=2016-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160515130707/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6700433/demi-lovato-confident-single-listen-stream|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌曲于2015年9月18日由[[好莱坞唱片|好莱坞唱片]]和[[小岛唱片|小岛唱片]]于[[亚马逊公司|亚马逊]]等数字零售平台发行。歌曲由洛瓦托、[[马克斯·马丁|马克斯·马丁]]、{{le|伊利亚·萨尔曼扎德|Ilya Salmanzadeh}}和[[沙凡·科提查|沙凡·科提查]]创作<ref name="warnerchapell">{{cite web|title=Confident: Song Details|url=http://se.warnerchappell.com/song-details/WW010516255000|publisher=Warner/Chapell Music|year=2015|accessdate=2015-09-20|archive-date=2017-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171210232554/http://se.warnerchappell.com/song-details/WW010516255000|dead-url=no}}</ref>。从商业层面看，歌曲于比利时、加拿大、捷克共和国、新西兰、苏格兰和美国跻身前30。

== 创作过程 ==
歌曲由洛瓦托、[[沙凡·科提查|沙凡·科提查]]、{{le|伊利亚·萨尔曼扎德|Ilya Salmanzadeh}}和[[马克斯·马丁|马克斯·马丁]]共同创作，莉亚和马克斯领衔制作<ref name="warnerchapell"/>。该曲是由“鼓点带动”<ref name="nylon">{{cite web|last=Handers|first=Mayden|title=Demi Lovato's real "Confident" in new song|url=http://www.nylon.com/articles/demi-lovato-confident-song|work=Nylon|accessdate=2015-09-20|date=2015-09-18|archive-date=2015-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923085856/http://www.nylon.com/articles/demi-lovato-confident-song|dead-url=no}}</ref>的[[流行乐|流行]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6700433/demi-lovato-confident-single-listen-stream|title=Demi Lovato Drops New Single 'Confident': Listen|last=Weiner|first=Natalie|accessdate=2015-12-18|date=2015-09-18|work=Billboard|archive-date=2015-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151212022224/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6700433/demi-lovato-confident-single-listen-stream|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[流行摇滚|摇滚]]歌曲，有关强权和自信<ref name="EW">{{cite web|last=Falcone|first=Dana Rose|title=Demi Lovato is 'Confident' on her new single|accessdate=2015-09-20|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/09/18/demi-lovato-confident-new-single|date=2015-09-18|work=Entertainment Weekly|archive-date=2015-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923031753/http://www.ew.com/article/2015/09/18/demi-lovato-confident-new-single|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌曲以[[降E小调|E{{flat}}小调]]写就，节拍为每分钟130拍，属[[韵律|复四拍]]。主唱音域从E{{flat}}{{sub|3}}低音，跨越到B{{flat}}{{sub|5}}高音<ref>{{cite web|title=Demi Lovato "Confident" Sheet Music|url=http://www.musicnotes.com/sheetmusic/mtd.asp?ppn=MN0155421|publisher=musicnotes.com via Universal Music Publishing Group|accessdate=2015-10-10|archive-date=2015-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151006105513/http://www.musicnotes.com/sheetmusic/mtd.asp?ppn=MN0155421|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 发行与评价 ==
2015年9月18日歌曲正式发行前夕<ref name="US Release">{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B014K4HZUO|title=Demi Lovato - Confident [Explicit]|work=Amazon Music|publisher=Amazon|date=2015-09-18|accessdate=2016-01-18}}</ref>，歌曲于2015年8月24日在网上泄露<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6671252/demi-lovato-song-confident-leaks-online-report|title=New Demi Lovato Song 'Confident' Leaks Online: Report|last=Weatherby|first=Taylor|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|date=2015-08-24|accessdate=2015-09-21|archive-date=2015-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923070928/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6671252/demi-lovato-song-confident-leaks-online-report|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[数码间谍|数码间谍]]正面评价该曲，表示“该曲是一首铜管乐器主宰的昂扬激进流行曲，乍一听她的歌声，便完全沉醉<ref>{{cite web|title=Demi Lovato takes no prisoners on her new single 'Confident'|url=http://www.digitalspy.com/music/news/a669221/demi-lovato-takes-no-prisoners-on-her-new-single-confident.html#~pq6F3t3YUuk0kV|publisher=Digital Spy|accessdate=2015-10-03|archive-date=2015-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151004160213/http://www.digitalspy.com/music/news/a669221/demi-lovato-takes-no-prisoners-on-her-new-single-confident.html#~pq6F3t3YUuk0kV|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”音乐时报（{{lang|en|Music Times}}）亦正面评价歌曲，表示“《玩美自信》展现了洛瓦托肆意洒脱、性感一面。凭着几番如雷鼓声和铜管乐器的号角声，《玩美自信》体现了全新的黛咪，肉眼所见之处没有心碎或挣扎迹象<ref>{{cite web|title=Demi Lovato's Post 'Cool for the Summer' Single 'Confident' Leaks Online|url=http://www.musictimes.com/articles/46106/20150824/demi-lovato-cool-summer-new-single-confident-leaks-stream.htm|publisher=Music Times|accessdate=2015-10-03|archive-date=2015-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151013080309/http://www.musictimes.com/articles/46106/20150824/demi-lovato-cool-summer-new-single-confident-leaks-stream.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

== 音乐录影带 ==
2015年10月9日，歌曲的音乐录影带在洛瓦托的[[Vevo|Vevo]]频道发布。录影带由[[罪恶之城_(电影)|罪恶之城]]、[[弯刀_(电影)|弯刀]]和《{{le|特工小子|Spy Kids (franchise)}}》系列导演[[罗伯特·罗德里格兹|罗伯特·罗德里格兹]]执导，洛瓦托、[[米歇尔·罗德里格兹|米歇尔·罗德里格兹]]、[[杰夫·法赫|杰夫·法赫]]、{{le|赞恩·霍尔茨|Zane Holtz}}和{{le|马可·扎罗|Marko Zaror}}出演<ref>{{cite web|title = Demi Lovato Kicks Major Ass In 'Confident' Music Video|url = http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/demi-lovato-confident-music-video_56180ddbe4b0e66ad4c7dbea|website = The Huffington Post|accessdate = 2015-10-17|date = 2015-10-09|last = Ledbetter|first = Carly|archive-date = 2015-10-12|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151012011909/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/demi-lovato-confident-music-video_56180ddbe4b0e66ad4c7dbea|dead-url = no}}</ref>。影片于[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]][[奥斯丁|奥斯丁]]{{le|捣蛋鬼工作室|Troublemaker Studios}}取景。就她在连续剧《{{le|杀出个黎明 (连续剧)|From Dusk till Dawn: The Series|杀出个黎明}}》饰演米娅一角与罗伯特·罗德里格兹会面后，洛瓦托让他执导音乐录影带。罗德里格兹表示：“我想让录影带看上去像部电影，不是一部东拼西凑、过分夸张的音乐录影带或电影片段，但实际上看上去是部间谍片。我认为将电影、想法和视觉效果整合到黛米·洛瓦托创作的这首歌曲中，是伟大的高潮<ref>{{cite web|title = The Behind-The-Scenes Story of Demi Lovato's 'Confident' Video|url = http://www.mtv.com/news/2351979/demi-lovato-confident-robert-rodriguez/|publisher = MTV News|accessdate = 2015-10-17|archive-date = 2015-10-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151017051847/http://www.mtv.com/news/2351979/demi-lovato-confident-robert-rodriguez/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url = https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pfjK2xpf79k|title = Demi Lovato - Confident (Behind The Scenes)|date = 2015-10-14|accessdate = 2015-10-16|publisher = DemiLovatoVEVO|archive-date = 2015-10-15|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151015024929/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pfjK2xpf79k&gl=US&hl=en|dead-url = no}}</ref>。”

视频开头，洛瓦托关进戒备森严的监狱，却因背叛米歇尔·罗德里格兹所饰角色而得到一位美军将军[[特赦|特赦]]。派去逮捕罗德里格兹时，洛瓦托很快意识到罗德里格兹搶先一步逃跑。警方试图将洛瓦托押回监狱，遭到尝试截下罗德里格兹的洛瓦托回击。罗德里格兹击败洛瓦托，洛瓦托在囚犯大巴士上被警方俘获。然而，她将警察打到失去自由，挣脱束缚，跳进罗德里格兹的拖车。快要大打出手，两人才意识到将军玩弄了她们（还{{le|人体烙印|Human branding|烙下印记}}），于是联手逮捕将军。后来警方揭示将军是[[诈骗|诈骗犯]]，洛瓦托和罗德里格兹告别，乘着各自的摩托车扬长离去<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cwLRQn61oUY|title=Demi Lovato - Confident (Official Video)|publisher=YouTube|accessdate=2015-10-10|date=2015-10-09|archive-date=2015-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151011054623/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cwLRQn61oUY&gl=US&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 现场表演 ==
2015年10月15日，洛瓦托在纽约一家同性恋酒吧首次表演该曲<ref>{{cite news|title=Demi Lovato Performs 'Confident' at Gay Bar -- Introduced by Nick Jonas!|work=Billboard|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6730794/demi-lovato-confident-gay-bar-nick-Jonas|accessdate=2015-10-18|date=2015-10-16|archive-date=2015-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151018175208/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6730794/demi-lovato-confident-gay-bar-nick-jonas|dead-url=no}}</ref>。为庆祝个人第五张专辑《{{le|玩美自信 (专辑)|Confident (album)}}》盛大发售，翌日，洛瓦托在[[時報廣場|时代广场]]不插电表演该曲，粉丝惊喜不已<ref>{{cite web|last=Martin|first=Macy Daniela|title=Watch Demi Lovato's Surprise Times Square Performance of "Confident"|url=http://www.popsugar.com/latina/Demi-Lovato-NYC-Surprise-Performance-Confident-Video-38789746|accessdate=2015-10-18|work=PopSugar|date=2015-10-17|archive-date=2015-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017233507/http://www.popsugar.com/latina/Demi-Lovato-NYC-Surprise-Performance-Confident-Video-38789746|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月17日，洛瓦托在{{le|周六夜现场 (第四十一季)|Saturday Night Live (season 41)|第四十一季}}《[[周六夜现场|周六夜现场]]》串烧演绎《嗨翻酷暑》和《玩美自信》<ref>{{cite news|last1=Kreps|first1=Daniel|title=See Demi Lovato's Confident 'SNL' Performances|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/tv/news/see-demi-lovatos-confident-snl-performances-20151018|accessdate=2015-10-19|work=[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]]|publisher=|date=2015-10-18|archive-date=2015-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151018232753/http://www.rollingstone.com/tv/news/see-demi-lovatos-confident-snl-performances-20151018|dead-url=no}}</ref>，又于10月29日的《[[早安美国|早安美国]]》和次日的《[[今夜秀|今夜秀]]》演唱歌曲<ref>{{cite web|last=Gracie|first=Bianca|url=http://www.idolator.com/7613268/demi-lovato-performs-confident-on-good-morning-america-watch|title=Demi Lovato Performs "Confident" On 'Good Morning America': Watch|work=Idolator|accessdate=2015-11-02|date=2015-10-29}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Peters|first=Mitchell|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6746256/demi-lovato-jimmy-fallon-confirm-confident-bff-status-on-tonight-show|work=Billboard|title=Demi Lovato and Jimmy Fallon Confirm BFF Status on 'Tonight Show': Watch|accessdate=2015-11-02|date=2015-10-31|archive-date=2015-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151104003318/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6746256/demi-lovato-jimmy-fallon-confirm-confident-bff-status-on-tonight-show|dead-url=no}}</ref>。11月6日，她于《{{le|瑞典偶像|Idol (Swedish TV series)}}》演绎歌曲<ref>{{cite web|last=Wass|first=Mike|url=http://www.idolator.com/7614196/demi-lovato-confident-swedish-idol|title=Demi Lovato Delivers A "Confident" Performance On 'Swedish Idol'|work=Idolator|accessdate=2015-11-07|date=2015-11-06}}</ref>。此外，洛瓦托还在11月8日的2015年[[BBC广播一台|BBC广播一台青少年大奖]]上表演歌曲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/article/34761657/one-direction-win-big-at-radio-1-teen-awards|title=One Direction win big at Radio 1 Teen Awards|publisher=BBC Newsbeat|date=2015-11-08|accessdate=2015-11-10|archive-date=2015-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151109012447/http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/article/34761657/one-direction-win-big-at-radio-1-teen-awards|dead-url=no}}</ref>。11月14日，歌曲入选洛瓦托2015年{{le|KBKS-FM|KBKS-FM|106.1 KISS FM}}秋季歌会歌单<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kissfmseattle.com/features/1061-kiss-fms-fall-ball-2015-1313/|title=106.1 KISS FM's Fall Ball 2015|work=106.1 KISS FM|date=2015-11-14|accessdate=2015-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117014109/http://www.kissfmseattle.com/features/1061-kiss-fms-fall-ball-2015-1313/|archive-date=2015-11-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。11月22日，洛瓦托携该曲亮相[[2015年全美音乐奖|2015年全美音乐奖]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/events/amas/6770312/demi-lovato-confident-amas-2015-american-music-awards|title=Demi Lovato Performs 'Confident' at the 2015 American Music Awards|last=Platon|first=Adelle|accessdate=2015-11-23|date=2015-11-22|work=Billboard|archive-date=2015-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151126014349/http://www.billboard.com/articles/events/amas/6770312/demi-lovato-confident-amas-2015-american-music-awards|dead-url=no}}</ref>，歌曲还入选她的{{le|2015年叮当球巡演|Jingle Ball Tour 2015}}歌单<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/6805703/iheartradio-z100-jingle-ball-new-york-demi-lovato-charlie-puth-fetty-wap-selena-gomez-msg|title=Jingle Ball NYC 2015: Demi Lovato Slays, Charlie Puth Home for Christmas & Fetty Wap Plays Santa|author=Michele Amabile Angermiller|work=Billboard|accessdate=2015-12-23|date=2015-12-12|archive-date=2015-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151215235149/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/6805703/iheartradio-z100-jingle-ball-new-york-demi-lovato-charlie-puth-fetty-wap-selena-gomez-msg|dead-url=no}}</ref>。以[[迪克·克拉克的跨年摇滚夜|迪克·克拉克的跨年摇滚夜]]主打歌手身份，洛瓦托于12月31日跨年夜于时代广场再度串烧演绎《嗨翻酷暑》和《玩美自信》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6828860/carrie-underwood-demi-lovato-luke-bryan-new-years-rockin-eve-times-square|title=Carrie Underwood, Demi Lovato, Luke Bryan and More Ring in 2016 in Times Square for 'New Year's Rockin' Eve'|work=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|accessdate=2016-01-30|date=2016-01-01|author=Michele Amabile Angermiller|archive-date=2016-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160130131608/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6828860/carrie-underwood-demi-lovato-luke-bryan-new-years-rockin-eve-times-square|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年3月3日，洛瓦托与《[[美国偶像|美国偶像]]》{{le|美国偶像 (第十五季)|American Idol (season 15)|最终季}}八强选手同台献唱歌曲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/recap/american-idol-season-15-episode-17|title=Watch Demi Lovato's 'Confident' Performance With 'American Idol' Top 10|author=Michele Amabile Angermiller|work=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|date=2016-03-03|accessdate=2016-03-09|archive-date=2016-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307020939/http://www.ew.com/recap/american-idol-season-15-episode-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌曲的另一个演唱版出现在2016年3月9日首播的第二期{{le|维多利亚的秘密泳装特辑|Victoria's Secret Swim Special}}中<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.popsugar.com/entertainment/Demi-Lovato-Victoria-Secret-Swim-Special-Performance-Video-40515801|title=Demi Lovato Victoria's Secret Swim Special Performance Video|first=Quinn|last=Keaney|work=PopSugar|date=2016-03-11|accessdate=2016-03-13|archive-date=2016-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160313083154/http://www.popsugar.com/entertainment/Demi-Lovato-Victoria-Secret-Swim-Special-Performance-Video-40515801|dead-url=no}}</ref>。5月14日，洛瓦托用歌曲为2016年的{{le|维戈探戈秀|Wango Tango}}开场<ref>{{cite web|url=http://onairwithryan.iheart.com/articles/headlines-496147/demi-lovato-opens-wango-tango-with-14713392/|title=Demi Lovato Opens Wango Tango With Powerhouse 'Confident' Performance|publisher=On Air with Ryan Seacrest|date=2016-05-14|accessdate=2016-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816021323/http://onairwithryan.iheart.com/articles/headlines-496147/demi-lovato-opens-wango-tango-with-14713392/|archive-date=2016-08-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。后来，洛瓦托在5月16日网上播出的{{le|詹姆斯·科登深夜秀|The Late Late Show with James Corden}}的拼车“卡拉OK”（{{lang|en|Carpool Karaoke}}）环节中演绎该曲<ref>{{cite web|title=Demi Lovato & Nick Jonas Carpool Karaoke|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0HeJKcynrGI|work=The Late Late Show with James Corden|publisher=YouTube|date=2016-05-16|accessdate=2016-06-01|archive-date=2016-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160602035726/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0HeJKcynrGI|dead-url=no}}</ref>。7月25日，洛瓦托在[[2016年民主党全国代表大会|2016年民主党全国代表大会]]上演唱歌曲，为[[希拉里·克林顿|希拉里·克林顿]]站台<ref name="Variety">{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2016/biz/news/demi-lovato-democratic-national-convention-1201822654/|title=Demi Lovato Performs AT DNC, Talks Mental Health Care|work=Variety|publisher=Penske Media Corporation|accessdate=2016-09-30|last=Johnson|first=Ted|date=2016-07-25|archive-date=2016-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161002075551/http://variety.com/2016/biz/news/demi-lovato-democratic-national-convention-1201822654/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月6日，歌手在[[安娜·温特|安娜·温特]]为克林顿举办的“历史制作”（{{lang|en|Made for History}}）时装筹款活动中，演绎《玩美自信》和《{{le|身体说|Body Say}}》两曲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://fashionista.com/2016/09/anna-wintour-hillary-clinton-fundraiser||title=ANNA WINTOUR AND CHELSEA CLINTON'S FASHION FUNDRAISER WAS FILLED WITH DRUMS, DANCING AND A-LIST|work=Fashionista|last=Fernandez|first=Chantal|date=2016-09-07|accessdate=2016-09-24}}</ref>。歌曲入选洛瓦托{{le|未来现在巡演|Future Now Tour}}歌单<ref>{{cite web|last=Ruggieri|first=Melissa|url=http://music.blog.ajc.com/2016/06/30/concert-review-and-photos-demi-lovato-and-nick-jonas-launch-tour-in-atlanta-with-heart-and-soul/|title=Demi Lovato and Nick Jonas launch tour in Atlanta with heart and soul|work=The Atlanta Journal-Constitution|date=2016-06-30|accessdate=2016-06-30|archive-date=2016-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160729070225/http://music.blog.ajc.com/2016/06/30/concert-review-and-photos-demi-lovato-and-nick-jonas-launch-tour-in-atlanta-with-heart-and-soul/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

